# CriticMarkup Syntax

Demonstration of [CriticMarkup](http://criticmarkup.com/) syntax in Kate.

* Addition: `{++ ++}`

For text{++ that has been added++}

* Deletion: `{-- --}`

For text{-- that has been deleted--}

* Substitution: `{~~ ~> ~~}`

For text {~~that was~>that has been~~} substituted

* Comment: `{>> <<}`

For interlinear comments

* Highlight: `{== ==}{>> <<}`

{==For text that is highlighted==}{>>@author With corresponding comments<<}
